OL,5, Schools in the UK should teach about   
OL,6, antisemitism as part of a wider drive  
OL,7, to tackle anti-Jewish hatred, a report 
OL,8, from a government adviser says.        
OL,10,FLord John Mann, a Labour MP who is the 
OL,11,FUK's antisemitism adviser, is urging   
OL,12,Fministers to work with social media    
OL,13,Fcompanies to eradicate hatred online.  
OL,15,FIt comes after reports of antisemitic  
OL,16,Fincidents reached a record high in the 
OL,17,FUK last year.                          
OL,19,FThe government said they supported     
OL,20,Fschools discussing antisemitism.       
